{"tid":1155366,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"莫奈印象派畫《乾草堆》以$8.6億元成交 成交價創莫奈作品成交價紀錄","createTime":"2019-05-15T01:51:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-15T02:13:37.000Z","uid":3090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"74491f8bb78b8e23c886b7358ddaa2546e1a0a3c","tid":1155366,"uid":3090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:51:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rK6jmyg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrK6jmyg.png&h=923eeb92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫奈《乾草堆》系列其中一幅作品，以$8.6億港元成交。(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n法國印象派大師莫奈（Claude Monet）《乾草堆》（Les Meules）系列其中一幅作品，周二在紐約一個拍賣會以1.107億美元（約8.6億港元）成交。蘇富比拍賣行表示，成交價創印象派畫作紀錄，亦創莫奈作品成交價紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n蘇富比並無公佈買家身份。匿名賣家1986年在佳士得拍賣會上以250萬美元（1,950萬港元）買得這幅作品。<br />\n<br />\n《乾草堆》系列畫作以「乾草堆」為主題，其中主要作品有25幅，均為布面油畫，於1890年夏末到次年春季，在法國吉維尼（Giverny）莫奈居所附近完成。這一系列作品以其對每天、每季不同時間光線的敏銳觀察而出名。<br />\n<br />\n現時，25幅《乾草堆》畫作中，8幅在私人手中，17幅在博物館。<br />\n<br />\n2016年佳士得拍賣另一幅《乾草堆》作品，當時以8,140萬美元（約6.3億港元）成交。<br />\n<br />\n此前，莫奈最高成交價的作品，是去年以8,469萬美元（6.6億港元）成交的《綻放的睡蓮》（Nymph&eacute;as en fleur）。<br />\n<br />\nHeavy網站／法新社"},{"pid":"e171e3876179bfd19e99fa0301d20e78d8fee0f8","tid":1155366,"uid":20867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T01:59:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://us.123rf.com/450wm/urfingus/urfingus1608/urfingus160800334/62286027-stock-illustration-money-laundering-concept-dollar-bills-flying-from-the-washing-machine-3d-illustration.jpg?ver=6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fus.123rf.com%2F450wm%2Furfingus%2Furfingus1608%2Furfingus160800334%2F62286027-stock-illustration-money-laundering-concept-dollar-bills-flying-from-the-washing-machine-3d-illustration.jpg%3Fver%3D6&h=cbd7f0aa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"416112d7a36dd117bdea4c0991db6cc7a942df17","tid":1155366,"uid":4826,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-15T02:01:58.000Z","msg":"屌喇嗎我都識畫啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgm